sources.description:
War hero recovers from amnesia and is confronted by his criminal past.

Original title: The Crooked Way (1949)

Director: Robert Florey
Writers: Richard H. Landau, Robert Monroe 

Main cast:
John Payne - Eddie Rice/Eddie Riccardi
Sonny Tufts - Vince Alexander
Ellen Drew - Nina Martin
Rhys Williams - Lieutenant Joe Williams

Genres: Film Noir, Crime, Drama, Thriller
Release date: April 22, 1949
Filming location: Los Angeles, California, USA
